												<p>Dear {!Step_Forward_Activity__c.Associate__c},</p>

												<p>Congratulations on gaining a conditional offer to Step Forward.</p>

												<p>One of the conditions of you being able to take up your place on the programme is that you submit some or all of the <strong>original</strong> documents below.&nbsp;</p>

												<p>This email is a reminder that you will not be able to gain a place on Step Forward without submitting them.</p>

												<p>Currently, we don&rsquo;t have all the documents we need from you and we won&rsquo;t be able to put you through to an interview with an employer unless you submit them.&nbsp;</p>

												<p>These original documents are:</p>

												<ul>
													<li>GCSE Maths Grade C and above or Level 2 equivalent</li>
												</ul>

												<p>AND</p>

												<ul>
													<li>GCSE English Language Grade C and above or Level 2 equivalent</li>
												</ul>

												<p>AND</p>

												<ul>
													<li>EU passport OR UK birth certificate OR UK driving license (provisional or full) with a UK birthplace in section 3 of the license</li>
												</ul>

												<p>OR</p>

												<ul>
													<li>NON-EU passport with passport stamp and letter from the Home Office stating right to remain and duration of stay in the UK.</li>
												</ul>

												<p>&nbsp;</p>

												<p>There are three ways you can submit your documents to us:</p>

												<p>&nbsp;</p>

												<table align="left" border="1" bordercolor="#ccc" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td><strong>2. Send your documents to us via recorded delivery&nbsp;</strong></td>
															<td><strong>3. Bring your documents to us in person&nbsp;</strong></td>
														</tr>
														<tr>
															<td style="vertical-align: top;">
															<p>Send your documents via recorded delivery to:</p>

															<div>Step Forward</div>

															<div>c/o Paige Trotman</div>

															<div>The Challenge</div>

															<div>39 York Road</div>

															<div>Elizabeth House</div>

															<div>Mezzanine Floor</div>

															<div>SE1 7NQ</div>
															</td>
															<td style="vertical-align: top;">
															<p>The Step Forward offices are open Mon &ndash; Fri 9am &ndash; 5pm</p>

															<p>&nbsp;</p>
															Email <a href="mailto:paige.trotman@the-challenge.org">paige.trotman@the-challenge.org</a> to book a time for you to come in</td>
														</tr>
														<tr>
															<td style="vertical-align: top;">Remember to include a return address so we can send your documents back to you&nbsp;</td>
															<td>&nbsp;</td>
														</tr>
														<tr>
															<td style="vertical-align: top;">Email step.forward@the-challenge.org to let us know the date you sent your documents</td>
															<td>&nbsp;</td>
														</tr>
														<tr>
